[
  {
    "id": "kp-4.1-01",
    "section": "4.1",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Geometrical terms & Polygons",
    "title_zh": "几何术语与多边形",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Geometry involves specific terms to describe shapes and their properties.\n\n**Vertices, edges, and faces** are the primary components of 3D shapes. A **vertex** (plural: vertices) is a corner where edges meet. An **edge** is a line where two faces meet. A **face** is a flat or curved surface.\n\n**Triangles** are classified by their sides and angles. An **Equilateral** triangle has all sides and angles equal ($60^{\\circ}$). An **Isosceles** triangle has two equal sides and two equal base angles. A **Scalene** triangle has no equal sides or angles.\n\n**Quadrilaterals** include common 4-sided shapes. A **Parallelogram** has two pairs of parallel sides. A **Rhombus** is a parallelogram with four equal sides. A **Trapezium** (US: Trapezoid) has at least one pair of parallel sides. A **Kite** has two pairs of adjacent equal sides and diagonals that intersect at $90^{\\circ}$.\n\n**Regular polygons** have all sides and all interior angles equal. Examples include a regular pentagon (5 sides) or a regular hexagon (6 sides).",
      "zh": "几何学使用特定的术语来描述形状及其性质。\n\n**顶点 (Vertex)、棱 (Edge) 和面 (Face)** 是三维形状的主要组成部分。顶点是棱相交的角。棱是两个面相交的线。面是平面或曲面。\n\n**三角形**根据边和角进行分类。**等边三角形 (Equilateral)** 的所有边和角都相等（均为 $60^{\\circ}$）。**等腰三角形 (Isosceles)** 有两条相等的边和两个相等的底角。**普通三角形 (Scalene)** 的边和角互不相等。\n\n**四边形**包括常见的四边形状。**平行四边形 (Parallelogram)** 有两组对边平行。**菱形 (Rhombus)** 是四条边都相等的平行四边形。**梯形 (Trapezium)** 至少有一组对边平行。**筝形 (Kite)** 有两组邻边相等，且对角线以 $90^{\\circ}$ 相交。\n\n**正多边形 (Regular polygon)** 的所有边和所有内角都相等。例如正五边形（5 条边）或正六边形（6 条边）。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-shape-prop",
        "label": "Identify properties of quadrilaterals",
        "label_zh": "识别四边形的性质",
        "description": "State the name or property (e.g., symmetry, diagonal properties) of a specific quadrilateral.",
        "description_zh": "写出特定四边形的名称或性质（如对称性、对角线性质）。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-shape-prop",
        "question": "A quadrilateral has four equal sides and no right angles. Write down the mathematical name of this quadrilateral.",
        "question_zh": "一个四边形有四条相等的边，且没有直角。写出该四边形的数学名称。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Consider shapes with four equal sides. These are either a Square or a Rhombus.\n**Step 2:** Check the angle property. Since it has no right angles, it cannot be a square.\n**Conclusion:** The shape is a Rhombus.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 考虑有四条相等边的形状。这可能是正方形或菱形。\n**步骤2：** 检查角度性质。因为它没有直角，所以不可能是正方形。\n**结论：** 该形状是菱形 (Rhombus)。",
        "source": "0580/11/M/J/20"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "Which property is true for all parallelograms?",
        "q_zh": "下列哪项性质对所有平行四边形都成立？",
        "o": [
          "All four sides are equal",
          "Diagonals intersect at $90^{\\circ}$",
          "Opposite angles are equal",
          "All angles are $90^{\\circ}$"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "In a parallelogram, opposite sides are parallel and equal, and opposite angles are equal. Diagonals bisect each other but do not necessarily meet at $90^{\\circ}$ (unless it's a rhombus).",
        "e_zh": "在平行四边形中，对边平行且相等，对角相等。对角线互相平分，但不一定以 $90^{\\circ}$ 相交（除非是菱形）。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [
      "geom-terms",
      "shapes-2d"
    ],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-4.2-01",
    "section": "4.2",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Geometrical constructions",
    "title_zh": "几何作图",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Construction uses a ruler and a pair of compasses to draw accurate shapes without measuring angles directly.\n\n**Perpendicular bisector** of a line segment $AB$ is a line that passes through the midpoint of $AB$ at $90^{\\circ}$. To construct it, draw two arcs of the same radius centered at $A$ and $B$, then join the points where the arcs intersect.\n\n**Angle bisector** divides an angle into two equal parts. To construct it, draw an arc centered at the vertex to cross both arms, then draw two arcs from those intersections to find a point in the middle, and join it to the vertex.\n\n**Constructing triangles** can be done given three sides (SSS) using compasses, or two sides and an angle (SAS) using a protractor and ruler.",
      "zh": "作图是指使用直尺和圆规准确地绘制形状，而不直接测量角度。\n\n**垂直平分线 (Perpendicular bisector)** 是指以 $90^{\\circ}$ 通过线段 $AB$ 中点的直线。作图方法：分别以 $A$ 和 $B$ 为圆心，以相同的半径画弧，连接两个交点。\n\n**角平分线 (Angle bisector)** 将一个角分成两个相等的部分。作图方法：以顶点为圆心画弧与角的两边相交，再分别以交点为圆心画弧找到中间的交点，最后将其与顶点连接。\n\n**三角形作图**：已知三边 (SSS) 时可使用圆规；已知两边一角 (SAS) 时可使用量角器和直尺。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-construct-bisect",
        "label": "Construct bisectors",
        "label_zh": "绘制平分线",
        "description": "Draw the perpendicular bisector of a line or the bisector of an angle using a compass and ruler.",
        "description_zh": "使用圆规和直尺绘制线段的垂直平分线或角的平分线。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-construct-bisect",
        "question": "Using a ruler and compasses only, construct the perpendicular bisector of the line $XY$. Show all your construction arcs.",
        "question_zh": "仅使用直尺和圆规，绘制线段 $XY$ 的垂直平分线。保留所有作图痕迹（弧线）。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Place the compass point on $X$ and open it to more than half the length of $XY$. Draw arcs above and below the line.\n**Step 2:** Keeping the same compass width, place the point on $Y$ and draw arcs to intersect the first two.\n**Step 3:** Draw a straight line through the two intersection points. This line is the perpendicular bisector.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 将圆规针尖放在 $X$ 点，打开至超过 $XY$ 长度的一半。在直线上下各画一段弧。\n**步骤2：** 保持圆规宽度不变，将针尖放在 $Y$ 点，画弧与前两段弧相交。\n**步骤3：** 用直尺连接两个交点。这条直线即为垂直平分线。",
        "source": "Adapted from 0580"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "What is the primary rule when showing construction in an exam?",
        "q_zh": "在考试中展示作图过程的首要规则是什么？",
        "o": [
          "Erase all arcs after finishing",
          "Use a pen for arcs",
          "Do not erase construction arcs",
          "Use a protractor for all angles"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "Exam markers need to see your construction arcs to award marks. Never erase them.",
        "e_zh": "阅卷老师需要看到你的作图弧线才能给分。千万不要擦掉它们。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [
      "constructions"
    ],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-4.3-01",
    "section": "4.3",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Scale drawings",
    "title_zh": "比例图",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Scale drawings represent real-world objects at a smaller or larger size while maintaining proportions.\n\n**Scale factors** are often given as ratios, like $1:100$ (where $1\\text{ cm}$ on the map represents $100\\text{ cm}$ or $1\\text{ m}$ in real life) or $1\\text{ cm to } 5\\text{ km}$.\n\nTo calculate **actual distance**, multiply the map distance by the scale factor. \n$$\\text{Actual} = \\text{Map} \\times \\text{Scale Factor}$$\n\nTo calculate **map distance**, divide the actual distance by the scale factor.\n$$\\text{Map} = \\frac{\\text{Actual}}{\\text{Scale Factor}}$$\n\nAlways ensure units are converted correctly (e.g., $1\\text{ km} = 100,000\\text{ cm}$).",
      "zh": "比例图在保持比例的同时，以更小或更大的尺寸表示现实世界中的物体。\n\n**比例尺 (Scale factor)** 通常以比率形式给出，例如 $1:100$（表示地图上的 $1\\text{ cm}$ 代表现实中的 $100\\text{ cm}$ 或 $1\\text{ m}$）或 $1\\text{ cm}$ 代表 $5\\text{ km}$。\n\n计算**实际距离**：将地图距离乘以比例尺因子。\n$$\\text{实际} = \\text{地图} \\times \\text{比例因子}$$\n\n计算**地图距离**：将实际距离除以比例尺因子。\n$$\\text{地图} = \\frac{\\text{实际}}{\\text{比例因子}}$$\n\n务必确保单位转换正确（例如，$1\\text{ km} = 100,000\\text{ cm}$）。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-scale-calc",
        "label": "Calculate distance from a scale",
        "label_zh": "根据比例尺计算距离",
        "description": "Given a scale and a measurement, find the actual distance or map distance.",
        "description_zh": "已知比例尺和测量值，求实际距离或地图距离。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-scale-calc",
        "question": "The scale of a map is $1:50,000$. The distance between two towns on the map is $8\\text{ cm}$. Calculate the actual distance in kilometres.",
        "question_zh": "地图比例尺为 $1:50,000$。地图上两个城镇之间的距离为 $8\\text{ cm}$。计算实际距离（以千米为单位）。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Calculate actual distance in cm.\n$8 \\times 50,000 = 400,000\\text{ cm}$\n**Step 2:** Convert cm to metres ($/100$).\n$400,000 / 100 = 4,000\\text{ m}$\n**Step 3:** Convert metres to kilometres ($/1000$).\n$4,000 / 1,000 = 4\\text{ km}$\n**Answer:** $4\\text{ km}$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 计算以厘米为单位的实际距离。\n$8 \\times 50,000 = 400,000\\text{ cm}$\n**步骤2：** 将厘米转换为米（除以 $100$）。\n$400,000 / 100 = 4,000\\text{ m}$\n**步骤3：** 将米转换为千米（除以 $1000$）。\n$4,000 / 1,000 = 4\\text{ km}$\n**答案：** $4\\text{ km}$",
        "source": "0580/22/M/J/18"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "A scale is $1\\text{ cm}$ to $2\\text{ km}$. How many centimetres represent $15\\text{ km}$?",
        "q_zh": "比例尺为 $1\\text{ cm}$ 代表 $2\\text{ km}$。多少厘米代表 $15\\text{ km}$？",
        "o": [
          "$30\\text{ cm}$",
          "$7.5\\text{ cm}$",
          "$15\\text{ cm}$",
          "$75\\text{ cm}$"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "Map distance = Actual distance / Scale = $15 / 2 = 7.5\\text{ cm}$.",
        "e_zh": "地图距离 = 实际距离 / 比例单位 = $15 / 2 = 7.5\\text{ cm}$。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [
      "scale-drawings"
    ],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-4.3-02",
    "section": "4.3",
    "order": 2,
    "title": "Bearings",
    "title_zh": "方位角",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Bearings are a way of measuring direction accurately using angles.\n\n**Three rules of bearings:**\n1. Measured from **North**.\n2. Measured **Clockwise**.\n3. Written as **Three figures** (e.g., $045^{\\circ}$ instead of $45^{\\circ}$).\n\n**Back bearings** (reverse direction) can be found by adding or subtracting $180^{\\circ}$. \n- If the original bearing is less than $180^{\\circ}$, add $180^{\\circ}$.\n- If the original bearing is more than $180^{\\circ}$, subtract $180^{\\circ}$.\nThis is because North lines are parallel, and back bearings use the property of interior angles.",
      "zh": "方位角是利用角度精确测量方向的方法。\n\n**方位角的三大规则：**\n1. 从**正北方向**开始测量。\n2. **顺时针**方向测量。\n3. 以**三位数字**书写（例如写成 $045^{\\circ}$ 而不是 $45^{\\circ}$）。\n\n**后向方位角 (Back bearings)**（反方向）可以通过加上或减去 $180^{\\circ}$ 来找到。\n- 如果原始方位角小于 $180^{\\circ}$，则加上 $180^{\\circ}$。\n- 如果原始方位角大于 $180^{\\circ}$，则减去 $180^{\\circ}$。\n这是因为各处的北线是平行的，后向方位角利用了同旁内角的性质。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-bearing-calc",
        "label": "Calculate a bearing",
        "label_zh": "计算方位角",
        "description": "Find the bearing of $B$ from $A$ using angle properties or a protractor.",
        "description_zh": "利用角度性质或量角器求 $B$ 相对于 $A$ 的方位角。"
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-back-bearing",
        "label": "Find a back bearing",
        "label_zh": "求后向方位角",
        "description": "Given the bearing of $B$ from $A$, find the bearing of $A$ from $B$.",
        "description_zh": "已知 $B$ 相对于 $A$ 的方位角，求 $A$ 相对于 $B$ 的方位角。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-back-bearing",
        "question": "The bearing of town $Q$ from town $P$ is $072^{\\circ}$. Find the bearing of $P$ from $Q$.",
        "question_zh": "城镇 $Q$ 相对于城镇 $P$ 的方位角是 $072^{\\circ}$。求 $P$ 相对于 $Q$ 的方位角。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** The given bearing is $72^{\\circ}$, which is less than $180^{\\circ}$.\n**Step 2:** Add $180^{\\circ}$ to find the back bearing.\n$072 + 180 = 252^{\\circ}$\n**Answer:** $252^{\\circ}$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 给定的方位角是 $72^{\\circ}$，小于 $180^{\\circ}$。\n**步骤2：** 加上 $180^{\\circ}$ 得到后向方位角。\n$072 + 180 = 252^{\\circ}$\n**答案：** $252^{\\circ}$",
        "source": "0580/21/O/N/19"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "What is the bearing of South-West?",
        "q_zh": "西南方向的方位角是多少？",
        "o": [
          "$045^{\\circ}$",
          "$135^{\\circ}$",
          "$225^{\\circ}$",
          "$315^{\\circ}$"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "South is $180^{\\circ}$ and West is $270^{\\circ}$. South-West is exactly in the middle: $(180 + 270) / 2 = 225^{\\circ}$.",
        "e_zh": "正南是 $180^{\\circ}$，正西是 $270^{\\circ}$。西南恰好在中间：$(180 + 270) / 2 = 225^{\\circ}$。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [
      "bearings"
    ],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-4.4-01",
    "section": "4.4",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Similarity and congruence",
    "title_zh": "相似与全等",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Shapes can be related through congruence or similarity.\n\n**Congruent** shapes are identical in size and shape. All corresponding sides and angles are equal. Conditions for triangle congruence: **SSS** (3 sides), **SAS** (2 sides, included angle), **ASA** (2 angles, 1 side), or **RHS** (Right-angle, Hypotenuse, Side).\n\n**Similar** shapes have the same shape but different sizes. One is an enlargement of the other. All corresponding angles are equal, and corresponding sides are in the same ratio (scale factor $k$).\n\nTriangles are similar if they have the same three angles (AAA).",
      "zh": "形状之间可以通过全等或相似建立联系。\n\n**全等 (Congruent)** 的形状在大小和形状上完全相同。所有对应的边和角都相等。三角形全等的条件：**SSS**（三边）、**SAS**（两边及其夹角）、**ASA**（两角及其一边）或 **RHS**（直角、斜边、一直边）。\n\n**相似 (Similar)** 的形状形状相同但大小不同。其中一个是另一个的放大。所有对应角相等，对应边成相同比例（比例因子 $k$）。\n\n如果两个三角形的三个角对应相等 (AAA)，则它们相似。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-similar-side",
        "label": "Calculate sides in similar triangles",
        "label_zh": "计算相似三角形的边长",
        "description": "Identify similar triangles and use the scale factor to find a missing side length.",
        "description_zh": "辨别相似三角形并利用比例因子求缺失的边长。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-similar-side",
        "question": "Triangle $ABC$ is similar to triangle $PQR$. $AB = 4\\text{ cm}$, $BC = 6\\text{ cm}$, and $PQ = 10\\text{ cm}$. Calculate the length of $QR$.",
        "question_zh": "三角形 $ABC$ 与三角形 $PQR$ 相似。$AB = 4\\text{ cm}$，$BC = 6\\text{ cm}$，$PQ = 10\\text{ cm}$。计算 $QR$ 的长度。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Find the scale factor using corresponding sides $AB$ and $PQ$.\n$k = PQ / AB = 10 / 4 = 2.5$\n**Step 2:** Multiply the corresponding side $BC$ by the scale factor to find $QR$.\n$QR = BC \\times 2.5 = 6 \\times 2.5 = 15\\text{ cm}$\n**Answer:** $15\\text{ cm}$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 利用对应边 $AB$ 和 $PQ$ 求比例因子。\n$k = PQ / AB = 10 / 4 = 2.5$\n**步骤2：** 将对应边 $BC$ 乘以比例因子求 $QR$。\n$QR = BC \\times 2.5 = 6 \\times 2.5 = 15\\text{ cm}$\n**答案：** $15\\text{ cm}$",
        "source": "Adapted from 0580"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "Two triangles are similar. Which of the following must be true?",
        "q_zh": "两个三角形相似。下列哪项必须成立？",
        "o": [
          "They have the same area",
          "They have the same perimeter",
          "Their corresponding angles are equal",
          "Their corresponding sides are equal"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "Similar shapes always have equal corresponding angles. Sides are proportional, not necessarily equal.",
        "e_zh": "相似形状的对应角总是相等。对应边成比例，但不一定相等。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [
      "similarity",
      "congruence"
    ],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-4.4-02",
    "section": "4.4",
    "order": 2,
    "title": "Area and volume of similar shapes",
    "title_zh": "相似形状的面积与体积",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "When a shape is enlarged by a linear scale factor $k$, its area and volume change differently.\n\n**Linear scale factor ($k$):** The ratio of corresponding lengths.\n$$k = \\frac{l_2}{l_1}$$\n\n**Area scale factor ($k^2$):** The ratio of corresponding areas.\n$$\\frac{A_2}{A_1} = k^2 = \\left(\\frac{l_2}{l_1}\\right)^2$$\n\n**Volume scale factor ($k^3$):** The ratio of corresponding volumes (or masses, if density is the same).\n$$\\frac{V_2}{V_1} = k^3 = \\left(\\frac{l_2}{l_1}\\right)^3$$\n\nThis is a very common topic in the Extended tier.",
      "zh": "当一个形状按长度比例因子 $k$ 放大时，其面积和体积的变化方式不同。\n\n**长度比例因子 ($k$)**：对应长度的比值。\n$$k = \\frac{l_2}{l_1}$$\n\n**面积比例因子 ($k^2$)**：对应面积的比值。\n$$\\frac{A_2}{A_1} = k^2 = \\left(\\frac{l_2}{l_1}\\right)^2$$\n\n**体积比例因子 ($k^3$)**：对应体积的比值（如果密度相同，也适用于质量比）。\n$$\\frac{V_2}{V_1} = k^3 = \\left(\\frac{l_2}{l_1}\\right)^3$$\n\n这是 Extended 考试中非常常见的考点。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-similar-area-vol",
        "label": "Relate length, area, and volume",
        "label_zh": "关联长度、面积与体积",
        "description": "Given two measurements (e.g., two lengths and one area), find the missing measurement (e.g., the other area).",
        "description_zh": "已知两个测量值（如两个长度和一个面积），求缺失的测量值（如另一个面积）。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-similar-area-vol",
        "question": "Two similar cylinders have heights of $3\\text{ cm}$ and $6\\text{ cm}$. The volume of the smaller cylinder is $20\\text{ cm}^3$. Calculate the volume of the larger cylinder.",
        "question_zh": "两个相似圆柱体的高度分别为 $3\\text{ cm}$ 和 $6\\text{ cm}$。较小圆柱体的体积为 $20\\text{ cm}^3$。计算较大圆柱体的体积。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Find the linear scale factor $k$.\n$k = 6 / 3 = 2$\n**Step 2:** Find the volume scale factor $k^3$.\n$k^3 = 2^3 = 8$\n**Step 3:** Multiply the smaller volume by $k^3$.\n$V_{\\text{large}} = 20 \\times 8 = 160\\text{ cm}^3$\n**Answer:** $160\\text{ cm}^3$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 求长度比例因子 $k$。\n$k = 6 / 3 = 2$\n**步骤2：** 求体积比例因子 $k^3$。\n$k^3 = 2^3 = 8$\n**步骤3：** 将较小体积乘以 $k^3$。\n$V_{\\text{大}} = 20 \\times 8 = 160\\text{ cm}^3$\n**答案：** $160\\text{ cm}^3$",
        "source": "0580/42/M/J/21"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "If the area of a shape is multiplied by $9$, by what factor has the length been multiplied?",
        "q_zh": "如果一个形状的面积乘以 $9$，那么长度乘以了多少？",
