        "a": 2,
        "e": "A parallelogram looks the same at $180^{\\circ}$ and $360^{\\circ}$, so the order is $2$. It has NO lines of symmetry.",
        "e_zh": "平行四边形在旋转 $180^{\\circ}$ 和 $360^{\\circ}$ 时看起来相同，所以阶数是 $2$。它没有对称轴。"
