  {
    "id": "kp-4.6-01",
    "section": "4.6",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Angles on lines and parallel lines",
    "title_zh": "直线与平行线上的角",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Basic angle rules are essential for solving geometry problems.\n\n**Angles on a straight line** add up to $180^{\\circ}$. **Angles around a point** add up to $360^{\\circ}$. **Vertically opposite angles** are equal.\n\nWhen a line (transversal) crosses **parallel lines**:\n- **Alternate angles** (Z-angles) are equal.\n- **Corresponding angles** (F-angles) are equal.\n- **Interior angles** (C-angles or co-interior) add up to $180^{\\circ}$.",
      "zh": "基础角度规则是解决几何问题的关键。\n\n**直线上的角**之和为 $180^{\\circ}$。**一点周围的角**之和为 $360^{\\circ}$。**对顶角**相等。\n\n当一条直线（截线）穿过**平行线**时：\n- **内错角 (Alternate angles)** (Z-型角) 相等。\n- **同位角 (Corresponding angles)** (F-型角) 相等。\n- **同旁内角 (Interior angles)** (C-型角) 之和为 $180^{\\circ}$。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-parallel-angle",
        "label": "Find angles in parallel lines",
        "label_zh": "求平行线中的角度",
        "description": "Find missing angles using the properties of parallel lines and give reasons.",
        "description_zh": "利用平行线的性质求缺失的角度并给出理由。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-parallel-angle",
        "question": "Two parallel lines are crossed by a transversal. An angle of $75^{\\circ}$ is given. Find the size of its co-interior angle.",
        "question_zh": "两条平行线被一条截线所截。已知一个角为 $75^{\\circ}$。求其同旁内角的大小。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Use the co-interior angle property: they sum to $180^{\\circ}$.\n**Step 2:** Subtract the given angle from $180^{\\circ}$.\n$180 - 75 = 105^{\\circ}$\n**Answer:** $105^{\\circ}$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 利用同旁内角性质：其和为 $180^{\\circ}$。\n**步骤2：** 从 $180^{\\circ}$ 中减去已知角。\n$180 - 75 = 105^{\\circ}$\n**答案：** $105^{\\circ}$",
        "source": "Adapted from 0580"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
