  {
    "id": "kp-4.6-02",
    "section": "4.6",
    "order": 2,
    "title": "Angles in polygons",
    "title_zh": "多边形中的角",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Polygon angle sums depend on the number of sides $n$.\n\n**Sum of interior angles** of any $n$-sided polygon is:\n$$(n-2) \\times 180^{\\circ}$$\nFor a regular polygon, one interior angle is $\\frac{(n-2) \\times 180}{n}$.\n\n**Sum of exterior angles** of any polygon is always **$360^{\\circ}$**.\nFor a regular polygon, one exterior angle is $\\frac{360}{n}$.\n\nInterior angle + Exterior angle = $180^{\\circ}$ (at any vertex).",
      "zh": "多边形的内角和取决于边数 $n$。\n\n任何 $n$ 边形的**内角和**为：\n$$(n-2) \\times 180^{\\circ}$$\n对于正多边形，每一个内角为 $\\frac{(n-2) \\times 180}{n}$。\n\n任何多边形的**外角和**始终为 **$360^{\\circ}$**。\n对于正多边形，每一个外角为 $\\frac{360}{n}$。\n\n在任何顶点处：内角 + 外角 = $180^{\\circ}$。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-polygon-sides",
        "label": "Find number of sides in a regular polygon",
        "label_zh": "求正多边形的边数",
        "description": "Given an interior or exterior angle, find the number of sides $n$.",
        "description_zh": "已知内角或外角，求边数 $n$。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-polygon-sides",
        "question": "A regular polygon has an interior angle of $140^{\\circ}$. Calculate the number of sides of this polygon.",
        "question_zh": "一个正多边形的内角为 $140^{\\circ}$。计算该多边形的边数。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Find the exterior angle first (easier method).\nExterior angle = $180 - 140 = 40^{\\circ}$\n**Step 2:** Use the exterior angle sum formula: $n = 360 / \\text{exterior angle}$.\n$n = 360 / 40 = 9$\n**Answer:** $9$ sides (Nonagon)",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 先求外角（更简便的方法）。\n外角 = $180 - 140 = 40^{\\circ}$\n**步骤2：** 利用外角和公式：$n = 360 / \\text{外角}$。\n$n = 360 / 40 = 9$\n**答案：** $9$ 条边（九边形）",
