  {
    "id": "kp-4.7-01",
    "section": "4.7",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Circle theorems (Core)",
    "title_zh": "圆定理（基础）",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Circle theorems describe properties of angles and lines in circles.\n\n**Angle at center:** The angle subtended by an arc at the center is twice the angle subtended at the circumference.\n\n**Angle in a semicircle:** The angle subtended by a diameter at the circumference is always $90^{\\circ}$.\n\n**Angles in the same segment:** Angles subtended by the same arc at the circumference are equal.\n\n**Cyclic quadrilateral:** The opposite angles of a quadrilateral whose vertices lie on a circle add up to $180^{\\circ}$.",
      "zh": "圆定理描述了圆内角度和直线的性质。\n\n**圆心角定理**：圆弧在圆心所对的角是它在圆周上所对的角的两倍。\n\n**半圆上的圆周角**：直径在圆周上所对的角始终为 $90^{\\circ}$。\n\n**同弧所对的圆周角**：同弧在圆周上所对的所有角都相等。\n\n**圆内接四边形**：顶点都在圆上的四边形，其对角之和为 $180^{\\circ}$。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-circle-angle",
        "label": "Find missing angles in circles",
        "label_zh": "求圆中缺失的角度",
        "description": "Calculate angles using circle theorems, often requiring multiple steps.",
        "description_zh": "利用圆定理计算角度，通常需要多个步骤。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-circle-angle",
        "question": "$A, B,$ and $C$ are points on a circle, center $O$. Angle $AOC = 110^{\\circ}$. Find angle $ABC$.",
        "question_zh": "$A, B, C$ 是圆心为 $O$ 的圆上的点。角 $AOC = 110^{\\circ}$。求角 $ABC$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Identify the theorem: Angle at the center is twice the angle at the circumference.\n**Step 2:** Angle $ABC = \\frac{1}{2} \\times \\text{Angle } AOC = 110 / 2 = 55^{\\circ}$.\n**Answer:** $55^{\\circ}$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 确定定理：圆心角是圆周角的两倍。\n**步骤2：** 角 $ABC = \\frac{1}{2} \\times$ 角 $AOC = 110 / 2 = 55^{\\circ}$。\n**答案：** $55^{\\circ}$",
        "source": "Adapted from 0580"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
