        "e_zh": "圆内接四边形的对角之和为 $180^{\\circ}$。$180 - 80 = 100^{\\circ}$。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [
      "circle-theorems"
    ],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-4.7-02",
    "section": "4.7",
    "order": 2,
    "title": "Tangents & Alternate Segment Theorem",
    "title_zh": "切线与弦切角定理",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Extended students must know additional theorems involving tangents.\n\n**Tangent-Radius property:** A tangent at any point on a circle is perpendicular ($90^{\\circ}$) to the radius through that point.\n\n**Tangents from an external point:** Two tangents drawn to a circle from the same external point are equal in length.\n\n**Alternate Segment Theorem:** The angle between a tangent and a chord through the point of contact is equal to the angle subtended by the chord in the alternate segment.",
      "zh": "Extended 学生必须掌握涉及切线的额外定理。\n\n**切线-半径性质**：圆上任意一点的切线都垂直于通过该点的半径（成 $90^{\\circ}$）。\n\n**切线长定理**：从圆外同一点向圆引出的两条切线长度相等。\n\n**弦切角定理 (Alternate Segment Theorem)**：切线与通过切点的弦所夹的角，等于该弦在另一圆周段（交错段）上所对的角。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-alt-segment",
        "label": "Apply Alternate Segment Theorem",
        "label_zh": "应用弦切角定理",
        "description": "Identify angles that are equal based on the relationship between a tangent and a chord.",
        "description_zh": "根据切线与弦的关系辨别相等的角。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-alt-segment",
        "question": "$T$ is a tangent to a circle at $A$. $AB$ is a chord. If the angle between the tangent $T$ and chord $AB$ is $40^{\\circ}$, find the angle in the alternate segment.",
        "question_zh": "$T$ 是圆在 $A$ 点的切线。$AB$ 是弦。如果切线 $T$ 与弦 $AB$ 之间的夹角为 $40^{\\circ}$，求交错段（弦所对）的角。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** According to the Alternate Segment Theorem, the angle between the tangent and the chord equals the angle in the alternate segment.\n**Answer:** $40^{\\circ}$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 根据弦切角定理，切线与弦的夹角等于该弦在交错段上所对的角。\n**答案：** $40^{\\circ}$",
        "source": "Adapted from 0580"
      }
