  {
    "id": "kp-4.8-01",
    "section": "4.8",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Loci",
    "title_zh": "轨迹",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "A **locus** (plural: loci) is a set of points that satisfy a specific rule.\n\n**Common Loci:**\n1. **Fixed distance from a point $P$:** A circle with center $P$.\n2. **Fixed distance from a line $AB$:** Two parallel lines on either side of $AB$, with semi-circles at the ends.\n3. **Equidistant from two points $A$ and $B$:** The perpendicular bisector of the line $AB$.\n4. **Equidistant from two intersecting lines:** The angle bisectors of the angles between the lines.\n\nIn exams, you often combine these to find a specific region (shading).",
      "zh": "**轨迹 (Locus)** 是满足特定规则的所有点的集合。\n\n**常见轨迹：**\n1. **到定点 $P$ 距离固定**：以 $P$ 为圆心的圆。\n2. **到定直线 $AB$ 距离固定**：$AB$ 两侧的两条平行线，末端为半圆。\n3. **到两点 $A$ 和 $B$ 距离相等**：线段 $AB$ 的垂直平分线。\n4. **到两条相交直线距离相等**：两条直线夹角的角平分线。\n\n在考试中，你通常需要结合这些规则来寻找特定区域（阴影部分）。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-locus-region",
        "label": "Shade a region based on loci",
        "label_zh": "根据轨迹阴影化区域",
        "description": "Construct multiple loci and shade the region that satisfies all conditions (e.g., closer to $A$ than $B$ AND within $5\\text{ cm}$ of $C$).",
        "description_zh": "绘制多个轨迹，并对满足所有条件的区域进行阴影处理（例如，离 $A$ 比离 $B$ 近，且到 $C$ 的距离在 $5\\text{ cm}$ 以内）。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-locus-region",
        "question": "Shade the region inside triangle $ABC$ that is closer to $AB$ than to $AC$.",
        "question_zh": "在三角形 $ABC$ 内部，对离 $AB$ 比离 $AC$ 近的区域进行阴影处理。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Identify the locus of points equidistant from two lines ($AB$ and $AC$). This is the angle bisector of angle $A$.\n**Step 2:** Construct the angle bisector of angle $BAC$.\n**Step 3:** The region closer to $AB$ is the side of the bisector 'next to' line $AB$. Shade this area inside the triangle.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 确定到两条直线（$AB$ 和 $AC$）距离相等的轨迹。这是角 $A$ 的角平分线。\n**步骤2：** 绘制角 $BAC$ 的平分线。\n**步骤3：** 离 $AB$ 更近的区域位于平分线靠近 $AB$ 的那一侧。在三角形内部对该区域进行阴影处理。",
        "source": "0580/21/M/J/18"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
